on><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rdeTio0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Welcome to this dump of random memes. Sometimes I make them themed, sometimes I don't. If you enjoy laughing without talking politics, getting away from the horrors of the world, or escaping reality, you’ll love following this page!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7CjUops.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I just like romance but trying to broaden my mind. I read lots of smart books when I was in college and school but they’re honestly weird or boring.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bVDKdT7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Backfired. Should’ve given him time to read.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VhyNPTb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This really kills the fantasy side of the story but it’s hilarious</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8ZAejZ1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Stay petty, potatoes.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xML6FML.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Time to call the cops</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sOpU9L0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Once again, stay petty</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vzN9wYZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I did this with two cats in my rental. Don’t worry, I kept it spotless. They never knew about them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZC8Bh0o.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Feeling a young? Have a kid guess your age. My five year old thinks I’m 59. I am not.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BeqGJVt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Makes a hilarious story</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tdlPlFp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Maybe he looks cuddly</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/p4BtHeu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If real, this is awesome</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1FzlHiA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Maybe it’s my dairy allergy</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HgInhb1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think people who are extremely in shape without much work are just blessed genetically</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RuUgvuG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Housework is just Sisyphus for adults</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cDFSC5g.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Humanity never changes, technology just gets better</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eweXwWA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Even on the paleo diet, depression exists?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4zytyQM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>People moved to the American plains just to get away from humans</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TUNmobd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Why do some people have to be party poopers?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xK8uLzn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Dream life</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fgRdsAM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I believe there’s something in the Bible about fallow fields. I forgot because I’m not a farmer.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6AlSO6T.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is boomer? I thought it was a complaint everyone had.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rQcOh15.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Some movies are being replayed on their anniversaries in theaters. Check it out.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eMOgQGo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’m not super into this movie (it’s good but not necessarily my cup of tea) but this is cute</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xfDvCqd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This cat has a quest. What does he want?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ccIp7OY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Give your life for theirs, I guess? Be Jesus?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yNtZFEr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Although funny, why ruin that poor bride’s wedding?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6PhGWRe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Peak girl brain</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aMXNQx9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This might work on a male boss</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3D4RHNr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sorry for what I said when my hormones were going nuts</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/W6sHtQp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Give me a piña colada and I’ll have two blocks of cheese</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xguYUMZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Why is this so true?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2U71SXs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My grandma once ate liver and onions in front of me, swearing they were delicious. Might as well have been crickets for how grossed out I was</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hWGLuF1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Getting in your biotics</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/L0qxYVL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Jake Peralta, is that you?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zyAxfaL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oops, forgot I was at the church potluck</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WBa71TH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Why yes I can!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AjHRx93.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>She’s just protecting you!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7lQzZKd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Probably would scream but so cute in pictures</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iF2JRV2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think this is what my husband sees when I’m having a freak out</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/f2NOmZt.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And I thought I was soooo cool</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FCFLmeB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I just throw them out</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cFUuWjR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Rich people will spend their money on anything but helping the truly needy</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/thmsUsk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I know what it stands for, you don’t have to tell me</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BJOQ2A0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I just enjoy the possibilities</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4RnIKGG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Mine are getting wise to me</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MEnzTCJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Where’s the problem?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jTv3awl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>She would</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o4PjGKA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Oh no!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4zJxe6s</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GigglySprinkleCupcake]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nine Inch Tails</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ikFOCWJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KPwJbJo.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ikFOCWJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AllAnusMorissette]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>ARE WE THE BAD GUYS - ECONOMIC TERRORISTS</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Xkp0wi5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JczNQnI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>SAY WHAT?</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Xkp0wi5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WellThereYouAre]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Trump is going to LOVE the Commission on Presidential Capacity</title><link>https: